## Anti-Patterns

| Avoid | Do Instead |
|---|---|
| Treating authorization as verifier evidence | Require per-cell evidence |
| Leaving staged work in the shared index | Gate promptly or unstage and hand off |
| Waking panes without mail context | Mail the packet first, then wake |
| Combining unrelated work units in one commit | Split payloads before verifier packets |
| Closing Beads issues without commit and attestation refs | Close with durable refs and sync |
